{"tid":2302479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：海洋公園能否再獲注資明年初揭盅","createTime":"2020-11-27T06:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T06:56:45.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"39933083c025d72d9e126fc7ea38524c55a0a9f7","tid":2302479,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n邱騰華指，保育及旅遊合併發展，需要投入大量資助，直指是一個好好合作機會，但對於日後海鮮舫的運作需要再作商量，稱未來不一定只做酒樓及賣海鮮；而目前也難以確實是否需要再作注資，但不希望為海洋公園帶來額外財務負擔。<br />\n今年5月海洋公園爆財困時，邱騰華曾指海洋公園現行最需要是「救亡，捱過呢個冬天」，亦指園方有責任重新定位，不可以過份依賴旅客；今日邱在記招上，再向海洋公園「進言」，指政府會專心專注發展海洋公園，海洋公園不能固步自封、單靠門票養動物，理應運用自身地理優勢發展；又稱對海洋公園推行發展「森度遊」等有正面評價。被問到政府會否再向海洋公園撥款，邱指要待明年1月，待海洋公園有轉型方案之後再交代。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201127/6M7Z72TV2RCWBGNUS5HCRP2JRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201127%2F6M7Z72TV2RCWBGNUS5HCRP2JRE%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpJBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=b94ad49d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201127%2F6M7Z72TV2RCWBGNUS5HCRP2JRE%2F&h=0d6b986f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201127/6M7Z72TV2RCWBGNUS5HCRP2JRE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kB3P5aD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkB3P5aD.png&h=450b05be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7624b57c9a30bd75f38296d47b1c3dc527729088","tid":2302479,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"屌你注就注啦懶係要考慮咁"},{"pid":"98377cd5dbfbf7f8462cda76f12ca07e5442c797","tid":2302479,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"劉鳴煒又夠鐘同777奶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d4ccf03ce58593e64500947772af7ffa01f0e8","tid":2302479,"uid":156652,"l